<h1 class="article-title">
<img alt="Open-access" class="logo-open-access" data-bs-toggle="tooltip" src="https://ds.scielo.org/img/logo-open-access.svg" data-original-title="by 4.0 "> Expropriation Backlashing and Tax Burden in Latin America<a id="shorten" href="#" class="short-link"><span class="sci-ico-link"></span></a>
</h1>
